<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>VAILAMTAHNAK AH KA RA CH260</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vai-lam-tahnak ah ka ra, Ka mitcaw chaw ka ngei lo, Pek awk zeihmanh
 ka ngei lo, Khamhnak tha bik ka hmuh ko.

[C1]
   Bawi Jesuh nangmah kan zumh, Na tha bik Kal-va-ry Tuufa
   Vai-lam-tahnak ah ka hung, Bawi Jesuh ka khamh ko sawh. 2. Nangmah kha
   saupi kan duh, Si-na-seh ka lungthur cang, &quot;Kan tawl lai, a chim hi
   bang,&quot; Dawtnak in Jesuh a ti.

[V2]
 Ka ngeihmi vialte kan pek, Ka hawi, chaw, thil a zapi, Ka thlarau, ka
 pum dihlak, A zungzal na fa ka si.

[C2]
   Bawi Jesuh nangmah kan zumh, Na tha bik Kal-va-ry Tuufa
   Vai-lam-tahnak ah ka hung, Bawi Jesuh ka khamh ko sawh. 2. Nangmah kha
   saupi kan duh, Si-na-seh ka lungthur cang, &quot;Kan tawl lai, a chim hi
   bang,&quot; Dawtnak in Jesuh a ti.

[V3]
 Bawipa biakamnak ka zumh, Na thi thletnak bia tha kha; Ka lung cu ka
 thumh ko cang, Nangmah he thih ka ngamh ko.

[C3]
   Bawi Jesuh nangmah kan zumh, Na tha bik Kal-va-ry Tuufa
   Vai-lam-tahnak ah ka hung, Bawi Jesuh ka khamh ko sawh. 2. Nangmah kha
   saupi kan duh, Si-na-seh ka lungthur cang, &quot;Kan tawl lai, a chim hi
   bang,&quot; Dawtnak in Jesuh a ti.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
